{"tid":1096812,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"4月 g嬸 金曲分享台 (￣﹁￣)","createTime":"2019-04-08T03:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T12:44:45.000Z","uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"741cb3685cc0f3da8e32088ffd957f6ba1dbc697","tid":1096812,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T03:26:28.000Z","msg":"上個po極少回應 要重貼 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ng嬸首先送上一首 〈少年行〉， 來自唱片 灰！色！都！市！ <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/n2ZRFpIwXvM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fn2ZRFpIwXvM&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=8c6e5c4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/n2ZRFpIwXvM</a>"},{"pid":"21ee1c25145ebd10fdd1cbfd89c770029fb42999","tid":1096812,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T03:28:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/B5nd3Alm284\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FB5nd3Alm284&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=efd2e226\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/B5nd3Alm284</a><br />\n<br />\n再黎齊聽 rock n roll？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abd5df202b8b074cc324928429c2604a11d6adb5","tid":1096812,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T03:40:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lf-BIY_1784\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Flf-BIY_1784&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=811b0d86\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lf-BIY_1784</a><br />\n<br />\n一首經典改編，原作來自樂隊歐洲合唱團（Europe）g嬸推薦 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8466d8f4653ff8e6607b433357e4977172edeea6","tid":1096812,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T04:08:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HIaczArMhjk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHIaczArMhjk&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=850ebc85\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HIaczArMhjk</a><br />\n<br />\n88年七大樂隊攜手合作，由港台牽線，為的是紀念香港廣播六十周年，因此歌詞中常提及DJ和收音機。旋律來自60年代受歡迎樂隊Teddy Robin &amp; The Playboys的老大哥泰迪羅賓，歌詞由三位樂隊御用詞人因葵、林夕、陳少琪合力填寫，編曲則交給個別樂隊自己負責，接力式獻唱，盡顯各自特色，聽眾各有所好，不過風格最鮮明的始終是壓軸的Raidas和達明一派，出場序如下 : Blue Jeans、太極、Beyond、Fundamental、Cocos、Raidas、達明一派。88年仍活躍的樂隊有Citybeat、(新)風雲、友誼接觸、民間傳奇、Crystal Zone等，基於不同原因並沒出現，有點可惜。《勁Band Super Jam》收錄在港台的《香港電台六十週年紀念》雜錦碟。"},{"pid":"efe94683efc3095d545fb5742074f9b83a2c3925","tid":1096812,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T04:17:39.000Z","msg":"小島樂隊 - 她的心<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/op3eOWK5-LM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fop3eOWK5-LM&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=fa0aef5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/op3eOWK5-LM</a>"},{"pid":"e0f1f73d7d33bea55c386a0343a4df9689cd1dd5","tid":1096812,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T04:43:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小島樂隊 - 她的心<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/op3eOWK5-LM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fop3eOWK5-LM&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=fa0aef5f\" target=\"_blank\"