r />\n黎兩首浮世繪，月滿繁星夜 上次貼過 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba391bd157032ce3e896235b0d5f98a1f446245f","tid":1096812,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T04:57:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小島樂隊 - 她的心<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/op3eOWK5-LM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fop3eOWK5-LM&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=fa0aef5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/op3eOWK5-LM</a></blockquote><br />\n哇薑汁兄今次咁早吖 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>放飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔怪得，搵到好野繼續貼喎 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b17c6e3acb85a521cf23e00168d68dbc89d7f951","tid":1096812,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T05:24:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QtszAra102I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQtszAra102I&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=5856c7ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QtszAra102I</a><br />\n<br />\n上面 勁band superjam 有提及友誼接觸，咁我就黎首友誼接觸啦，不過又係上次貼過 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"320b3e050ad0bc3f5b758f05ab721c979a227455","tid":1096812,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T01:59:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ly-ieVbJAT8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLy-ieVbJAT8&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=433f1e94\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ly-ieVbJAT8</a><br />\n<br />\n再黎首灰色都市內既 沒！法！拒！絕！ <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3f776eaa1bee972adbfa37566ab85767cb888b2","tid":1096812,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T02:02:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/QtszAra102I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQtszAra102I&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=5856c7ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QtszAra102I</a><br />\n<br />\n上面 勁band superjam 有提及友誼接觸，咁我就黎首友誼接觸啦，不過又係上次貼過 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IU73KIlpCbo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIU73KIlpCbo&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=500c79b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IU73KIlpCbo</a><br />\n<br />\n再黎多首友誼接觸，唱片名同歌名同名<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a499c4d3e98d1d7be75b611506ddaa35863a3016","tid":1096812,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T02:23:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_nBiF8YIr2w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_nBiF8YIr2w&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=fcf7f617\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_nBiF8YIr2w</a><br />\n<br />\n87年鄭敬基和陳少偉組成的風雲樂隊。鄭敬基跟Beyond的黃家駒同樣擁有一把沙啞聲線。大碟監製是今時今日已經是世界級的「David Richard Campbell」，三人包辦所有詞、曲、編、混音、樂器。當年主打三首歌曲，「Anita」、「Come Dance With Me」和「您」。前二者是輕快的Euro Beat節奏，後者是慢歌，鄭敬基磁性沙啞聲線用心演釋這首悅耳情歌，是全碟最精彩之作。雖然其他歌曲並沒有大熱，但詞曲均是水準之作，例如激昂勵志的發放聲量，哀怨悲涼的我被磨碎、睡吧。全碟運用了大量優美和先進的電子合成器演奏，唯一可惜是這張大碟的錄音比較尖銳和刺耳，影響聽感。樂隊出了一張大碟便解散了，鄭敬基出色的創作天份在其後日子表露無遺，可惜多年來在樂壇的日子始終沒有大紅大紫，實屬可惜。"},{"pid":"58677effc02651d8d9032ac6f1ec4cd9ad835fa7","tid":1096812,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T02:23:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/_nBiF8YIr2w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_nBiF8YIr2w&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=fcf7f617\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_nBiF8YIr2w</a><br />\n<br />\n87年鄭敬基和陳少偉組成的風雲樂隊。鄭敬基跟Beyond的黃家駒同樣擁有一把沙啞聲線。大碟監製是今時今日已經是世界級的「David Richard Campbell」，三人包辦所有詞、曲、編、混音、樂器。當年主打三首歌曲，「Anita」、「Come Dance With Me」和「您」。前二者是輕快的Euro Beat節奏，後者是慢歌，鄭敬基磁性沙啞聲線用心演釋這首悅耳情歌，是全碟最精彩之作。雖然其他歌曲並沒有大熱，但詞曲均是水準之作，例如激昂勵志的發放聲量，哀怨悲涼的我被磨碎、睡吧。全碟運用了大量優美和先進的電子合成器演奏，唯一可惜是這張大碟的錄音比較尖銳和刺耳，影響聽感。樂隊出了一張大碟便解散了，鄭敬基出色的創作天份在其後日子表露無遺，可惜多年來在樂壇的日子始終沒有大紅大紫，實屬可惜。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/d-JXuS0JpPI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fd-JXuS0JpPI&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=3564e73a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/d-JXuS0JpPI</a><br />\n<br />\n陳少偉87年離開風雲後，顆拍蔣志光及王利名組成新風雲樂隊。樂隊走電子強勁節拍，熱門歌曲包括「長恨歌」、「迷城」，其中「埋藏的太陽」是唯一的舒情靚歌。當年林振強、雨言、林夕也有為樂隊填詞。樂隊出了一張大碟「迷」便解散了，反而當年並不起眼的蔣志光，之後個人歌手發展後在樂壇大放異彩。"},{"pid":"cc02bf383cbf54d75adb2a631d01bf2e7c01fe9a","tid":1096812,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T06:00:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1IzCUkSXuL8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1IzCUkSXuL8&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=d15f368f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1IzCUkSXuL8</a><br />\n<br />\n蔣志光 拯救行動，應該係以前咁多首之中唯一快歌 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"263b36ad28428c8d8f9ce6bdb2864263e21e088e","tid":1096812,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T06:05:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lESSuKii0m0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlESSuKii0m0&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=023a00b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lESSuKii0m0</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rCIeXdXJhd4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrCIeXdXJhd4&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=7c350731\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rCIeXdXJhd4</a><br />\n<br />\n民間傳奇<br />\n<br />\n1987年嘉士伯流行音樂節憑「Forever Young」奪得冠軍。和Blue Jeans一樣，樂隊成員都是長髮披肩的前衛Rock友打扮。樂隊四人都是夾Band發燒友，有相豐富的現場表演經濟。1988年出了唯一的一張大碟，音樂風格和City Beat相似，都是走美式Hard Rock，其中一曲「未來主人翁」，是一首抒情加搖滾的勵志歌曲，是全碟最商業化的佳作。"},{"pid":"0e90f3f1b6bbdde97af7dbcb0f68a8b1ca857fe5","tid":1096812,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T06:16:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LBCC55dSTGM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLBCC55dSTGM&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=47870f8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LBCC55dSTGM</a><br />\n<br />\n瞿培瑛都係一碟歌手，又是屬於藝視唱片，大碟的賣點是「雜誌式封面」，將唱片封面設計到像「VOGUE」，唱片名字仲有個扮嘢法文名「La Mode De'88」，主打歌《木偶點唱機》是Eurobeat，歌詞唱齊Madonna、Michael Jackson、Donna Summer，瞿小姐都曾參加85年新秀 (杜德偉那屆)，唔知點解咁快就消失於樂壇。"},{"pid":"0c83adfe19d4567490ac736cf350562ae2be5258","tid":1096812,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T06:27:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">八十前 不禁政治禁鹹濕歌</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/g_zifp8M8a0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fg_zifp8M8a0&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=e30d0711\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/g_zifp8M8a0</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CbCBLcE8fkU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCbCBLcE8fkU&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=a0125635\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CbCBLcE8fkU</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XkFTDlePxDw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXkFTDlePxDw&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=1da1acba\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XkFTDlePxDw</a><br />\n<br />\n皇妃樂隊1985年成立，音樂態度走偏鋒，歌詞大多都關於性和對女人的渴求，高喊：「讓性愛解放！」和「此刻給我性慾發揮！」<br />\n<br />\n他們推出的第一張亦是唯一一張大碟《迷失的愛人》，講明是禁歌，所有電台都不會播放，大碟歌曲《同性戀Gay》、《讓性愛解放》、《娼妓》等等，因為歌詞太大膽露骨，完全是犯禁，不存在灰色地帶，順理成章成為禁歌，也不為奇。"},{"pid":"cf0d9cf7ab6ae423218985b7394fe54ff4f4e455","tid":1096812,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T16:38:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NYGUkAmokX0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNYGUkAmokX0&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=36f5c5c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NYGUkAmokX0</a><br />\n<br />\n繼續推chyna，回帶不相信 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d658b1d708b715d19f1fd9035a78edf98d59fe4","tid":1096812,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T02:56:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/w7uzs7WOlz4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fw7uzs7WOlz4&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=ba949f14\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/w7uzs7WOlz4</a><br />\n<br />\n今日心情躁躁地，就繼續搖擺啦！ <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/025919_097483ffec7dc8a1f0fb6d9467d2fa11.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F025919_097483ffec7dc8a1f0fb6d9467d2fa11.png&h=addbc80d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6e583e63a15814ea65b8f5a4b748dafc76251ab","tid":1096812,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T02:57:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ly-ieVbJAT8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLy-ieVbJAT8&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=433f1e94\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ly-ieVbJAT8</a><br />\n<br />\n我真係沒法拒絕喎 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"696ef66f7df0f390dff3178db0b3d953ec20e771","tid":1096812,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T02:58:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/q6r7vLQRxQA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fq6r7vLQRxQA&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=b8e1dc4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/q6r7vLQRxQA</a><br />\n<br />\n又再出現黑太陽？ <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5528a97dd00d90c27a82d5aa8c7be926de6392dc","tid":1096812,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T10:59:15.000Z","msg":"Blue Jeans - 不回頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TxWQTzXFtLA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTxWQTzXFtLA&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=4741aaac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TxWQTzXFtLA</a><br />\n法中情主題曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n昇哥曲、林夕詞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c394266862de9c06187ced99a276de7e1f1821f9","tid":1096812,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T12:44:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Blue Jeans - 不回頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TxWQTzXFtLA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTxWQTzXFtLA&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=4741aaac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TxWQTzXFtLA</a><br />\n法中情主題曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n昇哥曲、林夕詞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wjF9BR1ycnY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwjF9BR1ycnY&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=9ed0d5c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wjF9BR1ycnY</a><br />\n<br />\n電影版 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}